data.description: MLS# 271279 Seller willing to pay $18,000 in closing costs! Welcome to the stylish and modern 10319 W. Argent Rd. This thoughtfully updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home checks every box! Outside, a stately presence welcomes you with fresh exterior paint, a lush, manicured front yard with mature trees and an attached 2-car garage. Inside, you see the pride of ownership from wall to wall. The entire home was recently renovated with fresh paint, new lighting, new flooring, hardwood flooring and tile flooring. The living room has a cozy fireplace to cuddle up to as well as another wood burning fireplace in the bonus room. As you make your way to the kitchen you will see a brand new stairwell with shiplap accents. The bathrooms all have new vanities, sinks, fixtures, custom tile work, and gorgeous tile flooring. The kitchen has been completely renovated and expanded the layout to an open concept. This kitchen is a Chef’s dream! With all brand new stainless steel appliances, custom kitchen island with floating shelve accents. The backyard features a crystal blue pool that is fully fenced for extra protection. There is a storage shed and a great firepit to enjoy after a long day. This home has everything you could want and more, it’s a show-stopping MUST SEE!
